datoCmsEvent.title: Virtual Artistic Speed Dating for Keys with MeetCute LA

children.value: Join Katie Lindsay and Hannah Wolf of MeetCute for virtual artistic speed dating! Want to meet other members of Ring of Keys? Find new collaborators? Missing the bar conversations after a show? Want to meet some old friends and new strangers? Want to meet potential future collaborators? A quarantine creative partner? An accountability partner? Just want to chill with other artists? Join us at our virtual speed dating! We will facilitate community conversation as well as send you off into one-on-one rooms to connect.
